Symbol.Script_2D:
PEN gs_cont_pen
! ====================================================================== ! SCALE ! ======================================================================
call "2dDetailLevel_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters det2D
!!! ******************************** 2D SYMBOL
IF det2D = 1 THEN CALL "fa_SofaSymbol_CSo_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL iSofaSymbolType = SOFASYMBOL_RECTSIMPLE !! 1/200 IF det2D = 2 THEN CALL "fa_SofaSymbol_CSo_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL iSofaSymbolType = SOFASYMBOL_RECTSIMPLE !! 1/100 IF det2D = 4 THEN CALL "fa_SofaSymbol_CSo_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL !! Symbolic

CALL "fa_SofaSymbol_CSo_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL iSofaSymbolType = 0

RECT2 -a/2,-b/2,a/2,b/2 LINE2 -a/2,b/4,a/2,b/4 LINE2 -a/2,b/8*3,a/2,b/8*3
FILL gs_fill_type POLY2_B 5,2,gs_fill_pen,gs_back_pen, -a/2,-b/2,0, a/2,-b/2,0, a/2,b/2,0, -a/2,b/2,0, -a/2,-b/2,0
del 1
ENDIF
